onna get close to her mom?"],[4504,4612,"Take it, Anna."],[5034,5084,"Dad!"],[5405,5480,"What the..."],[5764,5918,"What did you put in Anna's drink?"],[6006,6172,"Dad, what are you doing?"],[6260,6381,"Fuck you, Charlie Clare!"],[6719,6802,"What was it?"],[6848,6906,"I didn't..."],[6969,7069,"Stop it!"]],"27":[[0,95,"Stop it!"],[266,383,"You okay, Isaac?"],[842,905,"That's fine."],[963,1071,"Your dad never liked me."],[1130,1180,"I get it."],[1476,1547,"Look what you did."],[1618,1726,"Apologize now!"],[1760,1939,"You're not even gonna ask me"],[1939,2022,"why I punched him?"],[2093,2173,"Do I need to?"],[2206,2335,"I know you too well."],[2335,2502,"You've always been jealous of Isaac."],[2615,2752,"Then why don't you ask him"],[2752,2873,"what he put in Anna's cup?"],[3161,3299,"Chris, that's the special medicine"],[3299,3390,"I got for Annabel"],[3390,3499,"to help with her birthmark."],[3632,3741,"Yeah, it is."],[3762,3970,"He's trying to help me with my birthmark,"],[4024,4320,"unlike you in your nonsense unicorn."],[4320,4479,"Trying to fix your birthmark?"],[4554,4646,"With today's tech,"],[4646,4750,"that's not even possible."],[4808,5021,"Not even the National Academy of Sciences"],[5021,5113,"can fix that."],[5171,5326,"And your fake medicine?"],[5509,5605,"It's probably harming her."],[5638,5722,"That's a lie!"],[5743,5914,"I spent a lot of time and money to get that"],[5914,5980,"for Annabel."],[6085,6318,"Charlie, Isaac means well,"],[6318,6427,"and you were in the wrong,"],[6427,6577,"so you owe him an apology."],[7290,7361,"It's fake."],[7557,7715,"And this medicine is probably going to"],[7715,7795,"damage her liver."],[7828,7982,"Are you trying to frame Isaac?"],[8091,8133,"Dad!"],[8162,8312,"You really let me down!"],[8370,8466,"Alright, alright."],[8566,8621,"It's fine."],[8712,8942,"Charlie's just jealous"],[8942,9071,"that I'm helping Annabel."],[9159,9217,"I get it."],[10352,10418,"You okay?"],[10439,10656,"If you touch my daughter again,"],[10